creator: Springbig
descriptionHtml: Looking for a place to keep all your digital communications in one secure place? How amazing would it be if you could use that hub to also place online orders and keep track of offers and rewards? Introducing the Greenside Recreational dynamic mobile app! Consolidate all your personal communications, discounts, and special offers into one convenient digital Greenside Recreational Hub.
descriptionShort: one-stop-shop for you to view important communications
